-- Thornburg raises $500 million from preferred stock
-- 
-- Thu Aug 30, 2007 10:28am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/08/30/businesspro-thornburg-preferred-dc-idUSWNAS318820070830

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - Thornburg Mortgage Inc. TMA.N, hurt 
recently by a credit squeeze, said on Thursday it raised $500 
million in an offering of convertible preferred stock. 

